| App-wide dropdown list            | `custom/Extension/application/Ext/Language/{en_us,vn_vn}.<prefix>_lists.php` (both)                             |
| BWC detail/edit/list view         | `custom/modules/<Module>/metadata/{detailviewdefs,editviewdefs,listviewdefs,searchdefs}.php`                    |
| Sidecar record / recordlist view  | `custom/Extension/modules/<Module>/Ext/clients/base/views/<view>/<view>.php` (or direct override)               |
| Subpanel (BWC)                    | `custom/Extension/modules/<Module>/Ext/Layoutdefs/<prefix>_<subpanel>.php`                                      |
| Subpanel (Sidecar)                | `custom/Extension/modules/<Module>/Ext/clients/base/layouts/subpanels/` or `custom/modules/<Module>/clients/base/layouts/subpanels/` |
| Custom REST endpoint (`DotbApi`)  | `custom/clients/base/api/<Name>Api.php`                                                                         |
| Outbound integration client       | `custom/include/<prefix>_<Service>Client.php`                                                                   |
| Hybrid module registration        | `$dotb_config['hybrid_modules']` in `config_override.php`                                                       |
| Credentials / endpoints / flags   | `config_override.php`                                                                                           |
| After ANY change                  | Admin → Repair → Quick Repair and Rebuild (+ Rebuild Relationships if relationships changed)                    |
